garage.model.ticket

Class Ticket

  • java.lang.Object
    • garage.model.ticket.Record
      • garage.model.ticket.Ticket
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CalculatePayment, java.io.Serializable

    public class Ticket
extends Record
implements CalculatePayment
    The Ticket class stores the customer's information including their vehicle. It is also logs the times of arrival and departure in order to calculate payment.

        Parameters:
        newCustomer - New customer associated with ticket.
        ticketNum - Unique ID to reference ticket.
        spaceNum - Space number assigned to the ticket.
